Package: clinicalsignificance
Type: Package
Title: Determine the Clinical Significance in Clinical Trials
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Benedikt", "Claus", , "b.claus@pedscience.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9501-0954"))
Description: In contrast to statistical significance, which answers the question 
    whether there exists a treatment effect or not, clinical significance 
    answers the question whether individual changes are meaningful for patients.
